=head1 NAME

mk-table-access - Parse slow query logs and print tables accessed by queries.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

  mk-table-access FILE

=head1 RISKS

mk-table-access only reads information.

At the time of this release, there are no known, critical bugs.

See also L<"BUGS">.

